k to the dry ingredients and mix until just combined."\u000a    },\u000a    {\u000a      "@type": "HowToStep",\u000a      "text": "Gently heat a non-stick frying pan and drop tablespoonfuls of the mixture from the point of the spoon onto the surface."\u000a    },\u000a    {\u000a      "@type": "HowToStep",\u000a      "text": "When bubbles start to burst on the top of the pikelets, turn them over and cook the second side until golden."\u000a    },\u000a    {\u000a      "@type": "HowToStep",\u000a      "text": "Place in a clean tea towel to cool."\u000a    },\u000a  "aggregateRating": {\u000a    "@type": "AggregateRating",\u000a    "ratingValue": "4.5",\u000a    "bestRating": "",\u000a    "worstRating": "",\u000a    "ratingCount": "20"\u000a  }\u000a  ]\u000a}\u000a</script>         <base href="https://edmondscooking.co.nz/"><!--[if lte IE 6]></base><![endif]-->         <title>Pikelets Recipe NZ | Edmonds Cooking</title>         <meta charset="utf-8">         <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>         <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">         <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">         <link rel="canonical" href="https://edmondscooking.co.nz/recipes/pancakes-and-pikelets/pikelets/">         <meta name="generator" content="SilverStripe - https://www.silverstripe.org" /> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /> <meta name="description" content="Pikelets are delicious with butter and jam or jam and whipped cream - or with sour cream, smoked salmon and dill. Try this kiwi recipe" />               <meta property="og:type" content="website">   <meta property="og:url" content="https://edmondscooking.co.nz/recipes/pancakes-and-pikelets/pikelets/"> <meta property="og:title" content="Pikelets Recipe NZ | Edmonds Cooking"> <meta name="twitter:title" content="Pikelets Recipe NZ | Edmonds Cooking">       <meta property="og:image" content="https://edmondscooking.co.nz